pve.GiveUpTips: Abandoning the dungeon will give you currently earned rewards only

pve.AwardDescription: All awards can be used in NBOX - Me - Backpack
pve.RuleText:
Dungeon Rule 
1. To enter the dungeon, you first need a weapon with the corresponding CE. Use the weapon and consume the corresponding NBOX to enter the dungeon and start idling. 
2. You can get Earth element rewards for developing dungeons, and Water element rewards when you idling. The higher the CE, the more advanced the dungeons, the better the rewards. 
3. You can get a platform upgrade voucher as the reward when you idling, which can be used in the platform directly. 
4. If you quit the dungeon during the idle process, you can get the rewards obtained during the current idle time.
pve.Name: The Exotics Pretender
pve.Overflowing: Experience is overflowing, please level up first
pve.CEUnsatisfied: Insufficient weapon CE, fail to enter

carddraw.LuckValueDescription: Lucky value reaching 100% must open quality A or the above weapons

uncharted.Description: Access to the secret world can idle for free to gain benefits
uncharted.Tips1: Idling time less than 3 hours can not receive the benefits
uncharted.Tips2: Idling time is too short to receive the benefits
uncharted.RuleText:
1. Players can participate in the idle game for free as long as they have any weapon 
2. When idling, it will automatically select a weapon with the highest current CE to use 
3. Players can only get idle benefits when they are online 
4. Idle benefits can be collected cumulatively, and the time for a single collection of benefits should be more than 3 hours
